{"tid":772862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲唔要switch可以讓比我","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T04:04:04.000Z","uid":181819,"like":12,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b221cf4273711e7be89d50ef4395dc1cc538397c","tid":772862,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買switch<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想打機放鬆下 買部switch千幾蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 千幾蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有switch讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有部switch玩下 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44b3a9df7d6c446b20bc96d3c930d6a9e420db2","tid":772862,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"柱?"},{"pid":"9677398e74494ea8f8a6439caf94018dca68bb07","tid":772862,"uid":117187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔睇演唱會喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e333bdbb85d46238b0dabc16a517984b66a193","tid":772862,"uid":80015,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"網上乞食"},{"pid":"7ac3e63d08413f24dfa0bb97e1ea21a73f3747c9","tid":772862,"uid":37107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"男定女?"